OL,3,CCervical smear scandal: Review ordered
OL,4,Cafter reviews - and no public inquiry
OL,6,FAfter the publication of three reviews
OL,7,Finto the Southern Trust cervical smear
OL,8,Fscandal, Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,9,Fhas ordered yet another review.
OL,11,FSome of those caught up in the scandal
OL,12,F- which found women with cancer had
OL,13,Fbeen given the all-clear - have told
OL,14,FUTV "time is up" and a public inquiry
OL,15,Fshould be called to get to the bottom
OL,16,Fof the debacle.
OL,18,FThree reports into the cervical smear
OL,19,Freview in the Southern Trust were
OL,20,Freleased on Wednesday.
