OL,3,CCervical smear scandal: Review ordered
OL,4,Cafter reviews - and no public inquiry
OL,6,FTwo concerned the trust's handling of
OL,7,Fboth screener underperformance and the
OL,8,FSerious Adverse Incident process. A
OL,9,Fpeer review into the Public Health
OL,10,FAgency (PHA) was also published.
OL,12,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt stopped
OL,13,Fshort of ordering a statutory public
OL,14,Finquiry despite the calls from
OL,15,Fcampaigners and MLAs.
OL,17,FInstead, another review into all
OL,18,Freports of screening failures will be
OL,19,Fcarried out in early 2026.
