OL,3,CCervical smear scandal: Review ordered
OL,4,Cafter reviews - and no public inquiry
OL,6,FAround 17,500 women in the Southern
OL,7,FTrust area who were screened between
OL,8,F2008 and 2021 had to have their
OL,9,Fresults rechecked after concerns were
OL,10,Fraised in a report by the Royal
OL,11,FCollege of Pathologists.
OL,13,FIn 2024, a trust review established
OL,14,Fthat eight women went on to develop
OL,15,Fcancer after their smears were misread.
OL,17,FTwo women, Lynsey Courtney and Erin
OL,18,FHarbinson, have since died of cervical
OL,19,Fcancer
