OL,3,CCervical smear scandal: Review ordered
OL,4,Cafter reviews - and no public inquiry
OL,6,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt announced
OL,7,Fon Wednesday that three reports
OL,8,Frelated to reviews of the failures had
OL,9,Fbeen published.
OL,11,FIn a statement he confirmed that he
OL,12,Fhas asked Professor Sir Frank
OL,13,FAtherton, former chief medical officer
OL,14,Ffor Wales, to conduct an expert review
OL,15,Fof all publications to date.
OL,17,FMr Nesbitt said the review findings
OL,18,Fwere expected in 2026 and would be
OL,19,Fdelivered directly to him "without any
OL,20,Finfluence" from officials in the
OL,21,FSouthern Trust or the PHA.
