OL,3,CCervical smear scandal: Review ordered
OL,4,Cafter reviews - and no public inquiry
OL,6,FThe minister said: "From the outset, I
OL,7,Fhave sought to understand what
OL,8,Fhappened, who was responsible, why it
OL,9,Fhappened and how can we prevent it
OL,10,Fhappening again.
OL,12,F"It is clear there were significant
OL,13,Fissues with the Southern Trust's
OL,14,Flaboratory including the management
OL,15,Fprocesses in place at a trust level
OL,16,Fand the quality assurance of the PHA
OL,17,Fwas inadequate.
OL,26,@nD@TOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
