OL,3,CCervical smear scandal: Review ordered
OL,4,Cafter reviews - and no public inquiry
OL,6,F"As to why it was allowed to continue
OL,7,Ffor so long, it is evident that the
OL,8,Fmethod for reviewing individuals'
OL,9,Fperformance within the trust was taken
OL,10,Fin isolation and that performance
OL,11,Ftrends over several years were not
OL,12,Fmonitored."
OL,14,FMr Nesbitt said cervical screening is
OL,15,Fno longer undertaken in the Southern
OL,16,FTrust and has been centralised in
OL,17,FBelfast.
