OL,3,CCervical smear scandal: Review ordered
OL,4,Cafter reviews - and no public inquiry
OL,6,FHeather Thompson from the group said:
OL,7,F"It's a real kick in the teeth.
OL,9,F"At the bottom of all of this is
OL,10,Fladies' lives, at the bottom of all of
OL,11,Fthis is bereaved families, people who
OL,12,Fhave got cancer, invasive procedures,
OL,13,Fsurgeries."
OL,15,FLeona Patterson added: "At what point
OL,16,Fdoes this stop with the reports? When
OL,17,Fdo we actually start getting answers?"
OL,19,FThe Southern Trust and PHA have
OL,20,Fapologised to those affected.
