OL,6,FDr Joanne McLean from the Public
OL,7,FHealth Agency said: "We have a number
OL,8,Fwoman who the SAI report shows because
OL,9,Fof issues with performance in the
OL,10,FTrust, they have come to harm.
OL,12,F"They have cancer at a more advanced
OL,13,Fstage than they otherwise may have had.
OL,15,F"Of course that is terrible, that is
OL,16,Freally sad and we are very sorry."
OL,18,FDr Stephen Austin from the Southern
OL,19,FTrust added: "It is really important
OL,20,Ffirst of all of all for the distress
OL,21,Fthat has been caused.
